akka.actor

Class UntypedActorWithUnrestrictedStash

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.actor.UntypedActor
      • akka.actor.UntypedActorWithUnrestrictedStash
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Actor, StashSupport, UnrestrictedStash

    public abstract class UntypedActorWithUnrestrictedStash
extends UntypedActor
implements UnrestrictedStash
    Actor base class with Stash that does not enforce any mailbox type. The proper mailbox has to be configured manually, and the mailbox should extend the DequeBasedMessageQueueSemantics marker trait. See UntypedActorWithStash for details on how Stash works.
